  <brief_title>Asthma Control-A &quot;Patient Follow up Programme&quot; Maintenance and Reliever Therapy in a Single Inhaler</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Patient Follow-up Program to Assess Asthma Control in Patients Using Symbicort® as Maintenance and Relief Therapy in a Single Inhaler (Symbicort® SMART: Budesonide/Formoterol 160/4.5 Mcg, 1 or 2 Inhalations x 2 Times Plus Additional Inhalations as Needed)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
