  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the change in patient's asthma symptom control using ACQ scores after 4 to 6
      weeks of Symbicort Turbuhaler (budesonide/ formoterol) in SMART approach.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
